The paper deals with the design and optimization of a limited feedback system for a single user with multiple-antenna transmitter and single-antenna receiver. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the optimization of transmission power control function at the base station, which is a control systems problem (cs.SY). The use of multiple antennas also involves signal processing and communication (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the asymptotic performance of the system, which is a topic in machine learning and statistics (cs.LG).
